1. Putnik je stigao na aerodrom* (nominativ) *ranije nego što je planirao. (The passenger arrived at the airport earlier than planned.)
2. Na aerodrom*u* (lokativ) se čeka red za prijavu prtljaga. (At the airport, there is a line for baggage check-in.)
3. Avion će sleteti na aerodrom*o* (akuzativ) u 14 časova. (The plane will land at the airport at 2 p.m.)
4. Na aerodrom*u* (dativ) se nalaze restorani i prodavnice. (There are restaurants and shops at the airport.)
5. Aerodromske* (genitiv) usluge su vrlo važne za putnike. (Airport services are very important for travelers.)
6. Letovi sa ovog aerodrom*a* (genitiv) su često ka kašnjenju. (Flights from this airport are often delayed.)
7. Sutradan će biti organizovan prevoz do aerodrom*a* (genitiv). (Transportation to the airport will be organized the next day.)